        Selling a Brisbane Property Near High-Voltage Transmission Lines or Powerlines
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Easement disclosure, electromagnetic-field questions, and the pricing reality for Brisbane homes affected by overhead infrastructure. A practical guide for sellers in suburbs where transmission corridors run through residential streets.
      </p>
    </div>
